  "detailed_description": "This is an Off Road game, not an arcade car race game! You can ride with different cars, SUVs, off road cars with 4X4 drive in open levels. The arrow help to you to find the best way. In the multiplayer section available all single player levels to head to head multiplayer race.<br />\r\nYou can host or join to multiplayer races.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n12 Single player levels.<br />\r\n12 PvP multiplayer levels<br />\r\nPvP multiplayer in different operation systems. At moment available the PC versions. Mac Linux version coming soon.<br />\r\n7 different cars with different setup, different driving assistance systems, ABS, ESP and TCS.<br />\r\nOpen Levels to find the best way, short cut track for the best time in some levels.<br />\r\nTPS, wheel, cockpit and external cameras for each cars and levels for the better view.<br />\r\nWorking dashboard.<br />\r\nDeformable cars.<br />\r\nRealistic car physics.",
  "about_the_game": "This is an Off Road game, not an arcade car race game! You can ride with different cars, SUVs, off road cars with 4X4 drive in open levels. The arrow help to you to find the best way. In the multiplayer section available all single player levels to head to head multiplayer race.<br />\r\nYou can host or join to multiplayer races.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n12 Single player levels.<br />\r\n12 PvP multiplayer levels<br />\r\nPvP multiplayer in different operation systems. At moment available the PC versions. Mac Linux version coming soon.<br />\r\n7 different cars with different setup, different driving assistance systems, ABS, ESP and TCS.<br />\r\nOpen Levels to find the best way, short cut track for the best time in some levels.<br />\r\nTPS, wheel, cockpit and external cameras for each cars and levels for the better view.<br />\r\nWorking dashboard.<br />\r\nDeformable cars.<br />\r\nRealistic car physics.",
